text: Rostislav Václavíček (7 December 1946 – 7 August 2022) was a Czech football player. He was a part of the 1980 Olympic Games, where Czechoslovakia won the gold medal. ==References== Category:1946 births Category:2022 deaths Category:Olympic gold medalists for Czechoslovakia Category:Czechoslovak footballers
